snippet.title: Master Builder for the Atari 2600
snippet.description:
Master Builder is an unique (Atari 2600 ) game.

But it has some bad flaws.

Like the controls which aren't terrible, but could be better and you can get stuck easily in a brick.

Now to the good things:

The graphics are good fir the year and there are many different ways to die.
